		"description": "A Full API Collection to get a city temperature.\n\n**Instant Weather** from any country in the World (ex: Paris, FR)\n\n<img src=\"https://content.pstmn.io/55ea49a5-9a87-40ff-aeec-d75b06f4fe43/aW1hZ2UucG5n\" width=\"148\" height=\"159\">",
